   <h2> [<font color="red">推荐书单</font>] 陈二狗的妖孽人生 BY: 烽火戏诸侯 <a href="forum.php?mod=viewthread&amp;tid=96254&amp;page=1&amp;authorid=52872&amp;mobile=2" rel="nofollow" class="blue" style="font-size:12px;font-weight:normal;margin-left:10px;">只看楼主</a> </h2> 
   <div class="plc cl" id="pid525327"> 
    <span class="avatar"><img src="http://www.binnao.com/uc_server/avatar.php?uid=52872&amp;size=small" style="width:32px;height:32px;" /></span> 
